  <title>NVRA instructions Maryland Chinese</title>
  <link>https://www.eac.gov/nvra-instructions-maryland-chinese</link>
  <description><![CDATA[
<span class="taxonomyterm18956feed">NVRA instructions Maryland Chinese</span>


            
<p><strong>马里兰州（ MARYLAND ）</strong></p>

<p><strong>更新日期：</strong><span><span><span><b><span>10-10-2021 </span></b></span></span></span></p>

<p><span><span><span><b><span>登记截止期限: </span></b><span>親身登記在下午5 時前，網上登記在下午11:59 前，郵寄在選舉日前21 天，以郵戳為準。 </span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span><span><span><b><span>6.</span></b><b> </b><b><span>身份证明号码。</span></b><span>如您目前無現時、有效的瑪里蘭州駕駛執照或MVA 身份卡，您必須填上您社會安全証號碼最後4 個數目字。准予官員要求您社會安全號碼最後4個數字的法定權力是選舉法第§ 3-202 款。號碼只用於登記和其他行政目的。它將予以保密。</span> </span></span></span></p>

<p><span><span><span><b><span>7.</span></b><b> </b><b><span>政党选择。</span></b><span>如果您想参加某个政党的初选，您必须登记加入该党。 </span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span><span><span><b><span>8.</span></b><b> </b><b><span>种族或民族。</span></b><span>留空。 </span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span><span><span><b><span>9.</span></b><b> </b><b><span>签名。</span></b><span>要在马里兰州登记，您必须： </span></span></span></span></p>

<ul>
	<li><span><span><span><span>是美国公民</span></span></span></span></li>
	<li><span><span><span><span>是马里兰州居民</span></span></span></span></li>
	<li><span><span><span><span>年齡至少16 歲*</span></span></span></span></li>
	<li><span><span><span><span>未有因精神傷健而受到監護，如有，法庭認為您無法溝通投票的意願</span></span></span></span></li>
	<li><span><span><span><span>没有犯买卖选票之罪</span></span></span></span></li>
	<li><span><span><span><span>没有犯重罪，或如果有，您已服完法院判决的监禁刑期，包括任何假释期或缓刑期。</span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>

<p><span><span><span><span>*您可以登記投票如您至少滿16 歲但不可以投票，除非到下一個大選時您至少已滿18 歲</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span><span><span><b><span>邮政地址：</span></b></span></span></span></p>

<p><span><span><span><span>State Board of Elections </span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span><span><span><span>P.O. Box 6486 </span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span><span><span><span>Annapolis, MD 21401-0486 </span></span></span></span></p>


      
